:: Choice1 [A_Family_photo] {"position":"725,875","size":"100,100"}
<div class="Choice1dialogue">
You chose the pile of family photos. Many contains people that is unfamiliar, but despite the blurred faces, you feel a sense of warmth as you run your thumb across surface of the paper.
 </div>
 
 <div class="Choice1dialogue">
You continue flipping through the pile of family photos, finding hundred of captured moments. Everyone is caught mid-action, absorbed in their own lives, eating together, laughing until there were tears, until you pause, spotting a handwritten letter underneath the last one.
 </div>
 
  <div class="Choice1dialogue">
"Mom and your Aunty Meggie, will be gone for while. Your Aunty Meggie wanted to go to that Harry Potter, so I'm going to take her there. Your sister will be watching you, and there's leftover spaghetti in the fridge. Don't put it in the oven!!"
 </div>
 
 
   </div>
 
 <div class="Yourbedroom_choices">
  
  <span class="_choices2">
    (link-goto: "A Toy piano" , "Choice2")
  </span>
  
    <span class="_choices3">
    (link-goto: "The cloest full of toys" , "Choice3")
  </span>
  
  </div>
  
</div>



:: Choice12 [Choice12] {"position":"600,600","size":"100,100"}
 <div class="Nochoice">
Regardless, any of your answers have no meaning now. This is the end, there is nothing for you to go back for. Nothing to fear or cry. Now come, follow me and I will take you where you need to be.
  </div>
  
   <span class="Followbutton">
    (link-goto: "Follow", "Followpath")
  </span>
  
  <audio autoplay loop style ="display:none">
<source src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/WindyVG-Starter/Chicago-s_Song_Project/main/music/SadHospital.mp3" type="audio/mpeg">
</audio>


:: Choice2 [Toy_Piano] {"position":"850,875","size":"100,100"}
<div class="Choice2dialogue">
You accidentally stepped on a toy piano, echoing a squeaky chime. You immediately stopped, observating closer than before.
 </div>
 
 <div class="Choice2dialogue">
"Wait." Your voice rings out from your throat, surpising you a bit but not enough to stop you from kneeling, letting your fingers toys the keys.
 </div>
 
 <div class="Choice2dialogue">
Each press hums a tune of the somewhere in the past. Regardless, how silly it sounds, it feels like you belong here, pressing every high and low keys, listening endlessly to a melody you can't seem to remember well. 
You paused, A voice begins to rise, soft at first, then grow clearer and closer, until it settles into that of a an older woman, gentle and maternal.
 </div>
 
  <div class="Choice2dialogue">
"This is the sharp key, and this, is the flat key."
 </div>
 
   <div class="Choice2dialogue">
"Grandpa said that music won't place a roof over your head, but you don’t gotta worry about that."
 </div>
 
    <div class="Choice2dialogue">
"Mama got you."
 </div>
 
 
    </div>
 
 <div class="Yourbedroom_choices">
  
  <span class="_choices1">
    (link-goto:  "A pile of family photos" , "Choice1")
  </span>
  
    <span class="_choices3">
    (link-goto: "The cloest full of toys" , "Choice3")
  </span>
  
  </div>
  
</div>


:: Choice3 [Cloest] {"position":"975,875","size":"100,100"}
<div class="Choice3dialogue">
The cloest; built only to contain crowded toys, clothes and other unnecessary things that children would not think much about. You step closer, easing the wooden door open, only to burst at the face with a bright, white light.
 </div>
 
     <span class="gochildhoodhomebutton ">
    (link-goto: "-->", "College")
  </span>


:: College [Firstdorm] {"position":"1175,725","size":"100,100"}
<div class="urvoice">
Within a blink of an eye, you appear in a messy college dorm. The walls was nearly covered with assignments, prints and sticky notes, the bed's sheet was uneven, and its lovely pillow, on the hard, wooden floor. The desk contain a open laptop, with some folders and notebooks, open and spread against the desk. You observed the room once more, you spot:

 </div>
 
 <div class="Collegechoicesbuttons">

  <span class="college1button">
    (link-goto: "A Manuscript paper", "Manuscriptpaper")
  </span>
  
  <span class="college2button">
