:: ExitDoor [exitdorm] {"position":"1175,600","size":"100,100"}
<div class=exitdormdialogue ">
You come face to face with a nicely decorated door. Its surface is covered with handmade DIY pieces and prints featuring a few famous artists and singers.
 </div>
 
<div class=exitdormdialogue ">
You firmly grab the handle of the dorm door, before twisting it open.
 </div>
 
 
     <span class="gochildhoodhomebutton ">
