:: No {"position":"1250,1200","size":"100,100"}
<div class="yourdialogue">
There was nothing, but a empty space. 
 </div>
 
   <div class="narrativedialogue">
If you say so. You will contunie on this path, with memories of the past that will come with you. The love of your passions and experiences will challenge you, but if it’s what you truly want, then so it shall be.
 </div>
 
 <div class="yourdialogue">
Ending 1
 </div>


:: Photoframe [LoverPhoto] {"position":"1300,600","size":"100,100"}
<div class=PhotoFramedialogue ">
You switch your attention to the simple photo. You gently presses against the fragile picture, scanning over the pretty lady with a beaming, lively, face. Everytime you blink at her, the more you begin to love and, oddly, feel an endearing sense of annoyance.
</div>
 
 <div class=PhotoFramedialogue ">
 "She always takes bad pictures of me every time she gets."
 </div>
 
 <div class=PhotoFramedialogue ">
 "One random day. We got into a augement over something dumb, then she said something even dumber."
 </div>
 
  <div class=PhotoFramedialogue ">
 "She said 'If I'm always on your mind and worrying you about my free spirit, you might as well marry me.' "
 </div>
 
 <div class=PhotoFramedialogue ">
 "What a odd way to say that your sign is a sagittarius."
 </div>
 
 
      </div>
 
 <div class="Yourbedroom_choices">
  
  <span class="_choices1">
    (link-goto:  "A Manuscript paper" , "Manuscriptpaper")
  </span>
  
    <span class="_choices3">
    (link-goto: "Dorm Door" , "ExitDoor")
  </span>
  
  </div>
  
</div>


:: Sleep [sleepcode] {"position":"1225,1025","size":"100,100"}
<div class="yourdialogue">
You trail your feet to the side of the bed, touching the jersey knit sheets before lifing your body weight, into the stiff surface. You place your hands above your abdomen, staring up to the ceiling, hearing nothing but your thoughts, until.
 </div>
 
 <div class="narrativedialogue">
In the end, there was nothing.
 </div>
 
 <div class="yourdialogue">
You didn't bother turning to the direction of that voice, besides, you don't even know where its yalpping is coming from.
 </div>
 
  <div class="narrativedialogue">
Do you regret reliving this? Those memories, those people, and you? Do you want them? Do you want me to take them away? I can.
 </div>
 
 
      </div>
 
 <div class="Beddialogue">
  
  <span class="Nobutton">
    (link-goto:  ' "No. I want them"' , "No")
  </span>
  
    <span class="Yesbutton">
    (link-goto: ' "Yes. I dont need them"' , "Yes")
  </span>
  
  </div>
  
</div>


