:: YourRoom [yourbedroom] {"position":"850,725","size":"100,100"}
<div class="Followchat">
A bright light flashes your eyes, blinding you just a bit before it settles. You remove your arm from your face, letting the surrounding areas consume every part of your view.
 </div>

 <div class="Followchat">
The room was quite lively, with toys scattered everywhere, the floor, the bed and stuffed poorly in the closet. On tables and drawers were sticked with colorful, goofy, sdtickers of cartoon characters. You continue wandering around, brushing your fingers on every surface until your eyes lay on:
 </div>
 
 
  </div>
 
